Usage: getExportMode [-help] [-fullPinout] [-implicitPortMapping]
                     [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-fullPinout                           # Output all pins. (bool, default=false)
-implicitPortMapping                  # Do implicit port mapping.
                                      # (bool, default=false)
-quiet                                # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault                           # Displays the current settings which are not default settings